*Chinese Traditional: 傳遞(1), 傳送 (2)
*Finnish: [[välittää]] (1), [[kuljettaa]] (1), [[ilmaista]] (2)
*German: [[befördern]] (1), [[übermitteln]] (2), [[übertragen]] (3)
*Dutch: [[overdragen]] (1), [[overbrengen]] (2)
*Spanish: [[transportar]] (1), [[trasladar]] (1), [[comunicar]] (2), [[expresar]] (2), [[transferir]] (3)
*Italian: [[trasportare]] (1), [[comunicare]] (2), [[exprimere]] (2)

